<paragraph blockId="4.[718,1267,312,1008]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">
<emphasis box="[718,814,313,336]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Discussão:</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="Klug, 1825" authorityName="Klug" authorityYear="1825" box="[822,1157,312,336]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="chrysostictus" subSpecies="chrysostictus">
<emphasis box="[822,1033,312,336]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Agrilus c. chrysostictus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="KLUG, J. C. F." box="[1042,1157,312,336]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" pagination="419 - 476" refId="ref15390" refString="KLUG, J. C. F. 1825. Entomologiae Brasilianae specimen alterum, sistens insectorum coleopterorum nondum descriptorum centuriam. Nova Acta Physico-Medica Academiae Caesareae- Leopoldino-Carolinae. Naturae Curiosorum, 12: 419 - 476." type="journal article" year="1825">Klug, 1825</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
foi descrito da 
<collectingCountry box="[778,879,344,368]" name="Argentina" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Argentina</collectingCountry>
. A esta espécie, após prévio exame dos tipos, deverá congregar três táxons: 
<taxonomicName authority="Obenberger, 1935" authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1935" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="comizon">
<emphasis box="[1082,1192,376,400]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">A. comizon</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="OBENBERGER, J." pageId="4" pageNumber="85" pagination="108 - 140" refId="ref15958" refString="OBENBERGER, J. 1935. De novis Agrili generis regionis Neotropicae speciebus (Col. Bupr.). Nove druhy krascc z rodu Agrilus Neotropicke oblasti. Acta Entomologica Musaei Nationalis Pragae, 13: 108 - 140." type="journal article" year="1935">Obenberger, 1935</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
do 
<collectingCountry box="[887,942,408,432]" name="Brazil" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Brasil</collectingCountry>
(localidade-tipo, Itaiaya, 
<collectingRegion country="Brazil" name="Rio de Janeiro" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Rio de Janeiro</collectingRegion>
, holótipo no 
<collectionCode box="[931,1011,440,464]" country="Czech Republic" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/hj12-2xm7" name="National Museum Prague" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">NMPC</collectionCode>
); 
<taxonomicName authority="Obenberger, 1935" authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1935" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lucullus">
<emphasis box="[1031,1134,440,464]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">A. lucullus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="OBENBERGER, J." pageId="4" pageNumber="85" pagination="108 - 140" refId="ref15958" refString="OBENBERGER, J. 1935. De novis Agrili generis regionis Neotropicae speciebus (Col. Bupr.). Nove druhy krascc z rodu Agrilus Neotropicke oblasti. Acta Entomologica Musaei Nationalis Pragae, 13: 108 - 140." type="journal article" year="1935">Obenberger, 1935</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
do 
<collectingCountry box="[812,867,472,496]" name="Brazil" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Brasil</collectingCountry>
(localidade-tipo: 
<emphasis box="[1044,1104,472,495]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">
<collectingRegion box="[1044,1100,472,495]" country="Brazil" name="Goias" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Goiás</collectingRegion>
,
</emphasis>
Jataí, 2 síntipos no 
<collectionCode box="[753,831,504,528]" country="Czech Republic" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/hj12-2xm7" name="National Museum Prague" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">NMPC</collectionCode>
) e 
<taxonomicName authority="Obenberger, 1935" authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1935" box="[865,1177,504,528]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="korsakovi">
<emphasis box="[865,983,504,528]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">A. korsakovi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="OBENBERGER, J." box="[991,1177,504,528]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" pagination="108 - 140" refId="ref15958" refString="OBENBERGER, J. 1935. De novis Agrili generis regionis Neotropicae speciebus (Col. Bupr.). Nove druhy krascc z rodu Agrilus Neotropicke oblasti. Acta Entomologica Musaei Nationalis Pragae, 13: 108 - 140." type="journal article" year="1935">Obenberger, 1935</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, descrito da 
<collectingCountry box="[749,850,536,560]" name="Argentina" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Argentina</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[860,944,536,560]" name="Paraguay" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Paraguai</collectingCountry>
e 
<collectingCountry box="[968,1026,536,560]" name="Brazil" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Brasil</collectingCountry>
. Desta espécie visualizamos quatro síntipos, dos quais três estão conservados no 
<collectionCode box="[718,795,600,624]" country="Czech Republic" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/hj12-2xm7" name="National Museum Prague" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">NMPC</collectionCode>
e um no 
<collectionCode box="[896,978,600,623]" country="Libya" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/49nc-28y0" name="Natural History Museum, Tripoli" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">NHML</collectionCode>
, todos provenientes do 
<collectingCountry name="Paraguay" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Paraguai</collectingCountry>
sem maior precisão de localidade. Não foi possível encontrar os tipos assinalados como provenientes do 
<collectingCountry box="[718,773,696,720]" name="Brazil" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Brasil</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion box="[785,883,696,720]" country="Brazil" name="Sao Paulo" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">São Paulo</collectingRegion>
) e da 
<collectingCountry box="[938,1039,696,720]" name="Argentina" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Argentina</collectingCountry>
, os quais poderiam, talvez, pertencer a outras formas. Por este motivo, para evitar possíveis confusões, torna-se necessária a criação do lectótipo aqui designado: 
<taxonomicName authority="Obenberger, 1935" authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1935" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="korsakovi">
<emphasis box="[974,1136,792,816]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Agrilus korsakovi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="OBENBERGER, J." pageId="4" pageNumber="85" pagination="108 - 140" refId="ref15958" refString="OBENBERGER, J. 1935. De novis Agrili generis regionis Neotropicae speciebus (Col. Bupr.). Nove druhy krascc z rodu Agrilus Neotropicke oblasti. Acta Entomologica Musaei Nationalis Pragae, 13: 108 - 140." type="journal article" year="1935">Obenberger, 1935</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<typeStatus box="[782,890,824,848]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Lectotypus</typeStatus>
<specimenCount box="[896,916,821,848]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[927,1016,824,848]" name="Paraguay" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">Paraguay</collectingCountry>
, J.F. Zikán leg. (
<collectionCode box="[1174,1255,824,848]" country="Czech Republic" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/hj12-2xm7" name="National Museum Prague" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">NMPC</collectionCode>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[718,1267,312,1008]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">
O exame da genitalia masculina dos tipos examinados de 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1935" box="[813,916,888,912]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lucullus">
<emphasis box="[813,916,888,912]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">A. lucullus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
e 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1935" box="[938,1058,888,912]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="korsakovi">
<emphasis box="[938,1058,888,912]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">A. korsakovi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(figs. 27 e 28), mostrou que não apresentam diferenças com 
<taxonomicName authority="Klug, 1825" authorityName="Klug" authorityYear="1825" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="chrysostictus" subSpecies="chrysostictus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="85">A. c. chrysostictus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="KLUG, J. C. F." box="[778,896,952,976]" pageId="4" pageNumber="85" pagination="419 - 476" refId="ref15390" refString="KLUG, J. C. F. 1825. Entomologiae Brasilianae specimen alterum, sistens insectorum coleopterorum nondum descriptorum centuriam. Nova Acta Physico-Medica Academiae Caesareae- Leopoldino-Carolinae. Naturae Curiosorum, 12: 419 - 476." type="journal article" year="1825">Klug, 1825</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(fig. 29), portanto, proponamos os seguintes sinônimos:
</paragraph>
